   www.campchaos.com/cartoons/napsterbad _ Warning: lots and lots
of bad language here. This page features the extremely popular
animated cartoons featuring fictional incarnations of Metallica's
Lars Ulrich and James Hetfield railing against their mortal foe,
Napster. ``Napster _ Bad!'' is becoming a Web cult classic.
</P>
