<SLUG> BC-TECHNOBUDDY0620-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Cell phone insanity is spreading, so here are some rules
 &HT;    By Bill Husted
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
