   BBN-PIAZZA (Undated) _ When he is at the plate, Mike Piazza
gives himself instant feedback. He processes the pitches he sees
and the way his swing feels. Beyond that, he keeps it simple. There
is too much analysis of hitting, the Mets catcher believes, and he
does not need it. By Tyler Kempner.
