 AM-ADD-NYT-BUDGET  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Add N.Y. Times News Service budget for papers of  &UR; TUESDAY &LR; , June
20.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BC-SCIENCE-NYT-BUDGET &LR;  &QL;
</P>
