<P>
   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ Scrub Energy Secretary Bill
Richardson as a potential running mate for Vice President Al Gore.
The Republican call for his resignation over the Los Alamos nuclear
lab security flap goes too far. But since another security lapse
has happened on his watch he is now tarnished and the Republicans
will gnaw at this like a dog with a bone. By MARIANNE MEANS.
