</P>
<P>
   OLY-MAIN _ Marietta's Chris Rodrigues (127 pounds, Greco-Roman)
of The Walker School has little chance at the upcoming wrestling
trials. That may be because he's the only high school student in
the competition. (Tierney, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25. WITH
LAYOUT
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   OLY-NOTE_ Inside the Olympics notebook. (Rosen, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 30.
</P>
