<HEADLINE>
QUIPS, QUIRKS AND QUOTES FROM THE CAMPAIGN TRAIL  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Political, Commentary and Humor Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 450-word material from The New York
Times Syndicate is for use by clients of The Economist.
